***************************************
version-4.2.0

SIGNIFICANT USER-VISIBLE CHANGES
 - `--skipDupRadar` is now replaced by `--skipMarkDup` to disable all duplicates processing

NEW FEATURES
  - conda recipe xengsort has been updated to fix broken dependencies when build the conda env
  - geniac.config:
      * singularityRunOptions set to empty (as autoMounts is noew set to true) 

BUG FIXES
 - test.config: set tmpDir to './'

